{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"d2c6949c-205f-44a6-9dfc-ae7b3b5c45dd","content":"You're on **MSTest 3.8.2** / .NET 9. Here's the recommended pattern:\n\n```csharp\n[TestClass]\npublic class MyServiceTests\n{\n    private readonly TestContext _testContext;\n    private MyService _service = null!;\n\n    // Constructor injection for TestContext (MSTest 3.3+)\n    public MyServiceTests(TestContext testContext)\n    {\n        _testContext = testContext;\n\n        // Synchronous setup goes here (lightweight only)\n    }\n\n    // Async initialization — runs before each test\n    [TestInitialize]\n    public async Task SetupAsync()\n    {\n        _service = await MyService.CreateAsync();\n    }\n\n    // Optional: one-time async class setup\n    [ClassInitialize]\n    public static async Task ClassInit(TestContext context)\n    {\n        await GlobalResource.InitializeAsync();\n    }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public async Task MyTest()\n    {\n        _testContext.WriteLine(\"Running test...\");\n        var result = await _service.DoWorkAsync();\n        Assert.IsNotNull(result);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n- **Constructor** — inject `TestContext`, do lightweight sync setup only. Runs before each test.\n- **`[TestInitialize]`** — use `async Task` for any async per-test setup.\n- **`[ClassInitialize]`** — use `async Task` for one-time async setup shared across all tests.\n- Keep the constructor cheap; heavy or async work belongs in `[TestInitialize]` / `[ClassInitialize]`.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"fa6e3fde-96f8-40e0-bc4f-f0b3d316d3e0","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"They're using MSTest 3.8.2 on .NET 9.0. In MSTest v3, constructor injection for `TestContext` is supported. Let me provide the recommended pattern.\n\nIn MSTest v3.8.2:\n- Constructor injection for `TestContext` is supported (added in MSTest 3.3+)\n- `[TestInitialize]` can be async (return `Task`)\n- `[ClassInitialize]` can be async\n\nLet me give a clear, concise answer with a code example.","outputTokens":519,"requestId":"602E:388A0A:256373B:27FFD86:6A0311E6"},"id":"f51e4ad2-aac5-457f-8dea-072bfbc4fc56","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:41:37.177Z","parentId":"b3f80180-6537-4dc8-a476-9e953df7bc1e"}
